    "body": "Hi @chrisvidal \n\nYou should use the \"url sync\" mechanism. This will make your url update as the parameters of the search are updated. Those url can then be bookmarked. [https://community.algolia.com/instantsearch.js/documentation/#initialization](In the documentation), there is a paragraph on how to get started with this mechanic.\n",
